      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay good to know. i was worried it was something serious. i also noticed i've been getting these weird headaches and feeling a bit dizzy when i stand up too fast... but i figured if it's just the lithium settling in it might pass. should i just drink more water to flush it out of my system or something?",
